- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel GAN conditioning scheme and a fully unsupervised training strategy. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves developing a model that can generate facial expressions. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper involves generating facial animations from images.
